{"tid":121783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尼日利亞怪事　女子聲稱懷孕兩年誕下山羊","createTime":"2017-02-15T13:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T13:04:17.000Z","uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e782f2d6aee8749a10485ecfd2c517d650435f","tid":121783,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170214/_2017021417425549434_detail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170214%2F_2017021417425549434_detail.jpg&h=c72dc220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n非洲尼日利亞傳媒報道，一名女子聲稱自己懷孕兩年後，誕下了一隻山羊。網上留傳的照片和攝錄片段，見到一隻類似羊的物體躺在石屎地上，周圍都是血，引來一堆人在周圍觀看，但不知道整件事是真還是假。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，這宗怪事在尼日利亞哈考特港發生，初時只在社交網站流傳，後來愈傳愈烈，連傳統的主流媒體例如《今日尼日利亞》、《尼日利亞日報》和《先驅報》也加入報道。<br />\n<br />\n星島日報報道<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/338378-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%B0%BC%E6%97%A5%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E%E6%80%AA%E4%BA%8B+%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E8%AA%95%E4%B8%8B%E5%B1%B1%E7%BE%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F338378-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2588%25A9%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%2580%25AA%25E4%25BA%258B%2B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%2581%25B2%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%2587%25B7%25E5%25AD%2595%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25AA%2595%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25BE%258A&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=59909482\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F338378-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2588%25A9%25E4%25BA%259E%25E6%2580%25AA%25E4%25BA%258B%2B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%2581%25B2%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%2587%25B7%25E5%25AD%2595%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25AA%2595%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25BE%258A&h=154bd7ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/338378-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%B0%BC%E6%97%A5%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E%E6%80%AA%E4%BA%8B+%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E8%AA%95%E4%B8%8B%E5%B1%B1%E7%BE%8A</a>"},{"pid":"08be9ffee7bf9b5bab664aa4565cadd9791fef46","tid":121783,"uid":62443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"應該係真，報章有報導。"},{"pid":"d6854ee88f13899eb7adea1daddad8f81cd90f52","tid":121783,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797fc7a0ebf422ff1f09c8d588de88ea05aabd51","tid":121783,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:17:06.000Z","msg":"又黎240p畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe64cd61f8660520960709903c523a0344451db","tid":121783,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:19:27.000Z","msg":"羊! 獸!"},{"pid":"a38d40d899cf8290239c89a4734b0188bac94fab","tid":121783,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:22:04.000Z","msg":"死左未"},{"pid":"6fda1e0cbe87ddc01f50e3919df3e50858741f08","tid":121783,"uid":84658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc411abc7b8e685b62e4709ada6ea3b620cee7d","tid":121783,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />